'''Letn<U+00ED> stadion''', formerly known as M<U+011B>stsk<U+00FD> stadion, is a multi-purpose [[stadium]] in [[Chomutov]], [[Czech Republic]]. Used primarily for [[association football|football]], it is the home stadium of [[FC Chomutov]]. The stadium holds 10,000 spectators, of which 1,000 can be seated.

